{"tid":1230593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣繼續撐香港　5000 人立法院外集會　陳家駒、鍾翰林、雞排妹出席","createTime":"2019-06-16T08:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T10:05:18.000Z","uid":39464,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"72e30109a069015e7cc6403ed6848dcb33a4b5b4","tid":1230593,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/ili-07_FyIKD_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fili-07_FyIKD_1200x0.png&h=5ab7594a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線今日再發起反送中遊行。在台灣，有當地民眾今天下午於立法院前舉行「反送中，撐香港」的集會。主辦單位表示，有約 5,000 名民眾參與。在周一凌晨衝突中被捕、正保釋候查的學生獨立聯盟召集人陳家駒，以及「學生動源」召集人鍾翰林，亦有現身台灣集會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/wwwwww_uE35U_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fwwwwww_uE35U_1200x0.png&h=d930f809&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在台香港學生及畢業生組成的逃犯條例關注組、台灣公民陣線和台灣青年民主協會，今日下午在立法院前發起「反送中，撐香港」集會。參與的人們除舉起「反送中」標語之外，亦有「拒絕一中、拒絕和平協議」、「台灣撐香港」的標語。<br />\n<br />\n主辦單位以國語、粵語和英文宣讀訴求聲明。他們譴責港府暴力鎮壓和平抗爭，要求港府承認 612 和平示威並非「暴動」，釋放被拘捕的抗爭者並停止司法追訴，並要求港府「撤回」修例，而非只是暫緩。<br />\n<br />\n他們亦要求台灣立法院發表「反送中聲明」，反對將台灣人移交中國，又要求台灣政府針對香港公務員、警察等來台進行嚴格管制，呼籲台灣與各國政府共同檢視香港民主、人權、法治狀況，阻止中國傷害香港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/反送中-台灣繼續撐香港-5000-立法院外集會-陳家駒-鍾翰林出席/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E6%92%90%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-5000-%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E5%A4%96%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83-%E9%99%B3%E5%AE%B6%E9%A7%92-%E9%8D%BE%E7%BF%B0%E6%9E%97%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%2F&d=p84ZIGfbRlzA5dgw%2Bb26WCVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=33e2683b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E6%92%90%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-5000-%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E5%A4%96%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83-%E9%99%B3%E5%AE%B6%E9%A7%92-%E9%8D%BE%E7%BF%B0%E6%9E%97%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%2F&h=13637973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/反送中-台灣繼續撐香港-5000-立法院外集會-陳家駒-鍾翰林出席/</a>"},{"pid":"2fa315ef1532eeb46ab9c21b05d127355dc07ccb","tid":1230593,"uid":7886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:57:56.000Z","msg":"一萬人為雨衣義士默哀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VRLMCG8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVRLMCG8.png&h=2fdf8aeb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6944f303ac70550b972cc61cd30ffe1496b9e6f","tid":1230593,"uid":194398,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:58:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f48866ce95f18486527e807c86e459575c9b52e3","tid":1230593,"uid":146621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T09:40:04.000Z","msg":"雞排妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96604c2e6443e4f857407c0006c650ad598df420","tid":1230593,"uid":76148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T09:44:26.000Z","msg":"鄭家純反修例"},{"pid":"a313b8bb2679f646b91593104782c64d0e5b6593","tid":1230593,"uid":227769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T09:47:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://chng.it/9czLYMPhM7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchng.it%2F9czLYMPhM7&d=p84ZIGfbRlzA5dgw%2Bb26WCVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=5a61440b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://chng.it/9czLYMPhM7</a><br />\n聯署要求英國當局撤銷林鄭老公同兩個仔個英國國籍"},{"pid":"64539199aff39cdaaf8a6c37dea313e7e6e9d7e8","tid":1230593,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T09:50:57.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜十萬人  高下立見"},{"pid":"817b0da7bd501288e0eebc5545ddf85f4b783b14","tid":1230593,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:05:18.000Z","msg":"雞排妹 <img 